"{\"uid\": \"artnews.com-art-news-news-bonhams-addresses-charity-scrutiny-paris-landmarks-become-olympic-venues-roland-dumas-dies-and-more-morning-links-for-july-8-2024-1234711620\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByThe Editors of ARTnews  To receive Morning Links in your inbox every weekday,\\u00a0sign\\u00a0up\\u00a0for ourBreakfast with ARTnewsnewsletter.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 24, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ARTnews\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ARTnews\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ARTnews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ARTnews\"}, {\"begin\": 37, \"end\": 44, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Early_Show\", \"score\": 0.9999305630551721, \"rank\": 6.944175764853492e-05, \"text\": \"Morning\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Early_Show\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Early_Show\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"YES OR NO?InThe Guardian, Dalya Alberge wrote aboutBonhamsclarifying how it conducts its charity auctions, after complaints that it was taking a \\\"buyer's premium\\\"-the charge added to the hammer price-from a good cause.\", \"from\": 130, \"to\": 348, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At a sale in support of the Teenage Cancer Trust charity, that took place last month, art dealer John Bradley asked if the auction house included the buyer's premium in \\\"all [the] proceeds\\\" mentioned in its catalogue.\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 566, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 377, \"end\": 397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teenage_Cancer_Trust\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Teenage Cancer Trust\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teenage_Cancer_Trust\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teenage_Cancer_Trust\"}, {\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Bradley_(United_States_Navy)\", \"score\": 0.7458002967871926, \"rank\": 0.17538277987678605, \"text\": \"John Bradley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Bradley_(United_States_Navy)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Bradley_(United_States_Navy)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bonhams' sale coordinator replied \\\"Buyer's premium will be payable and 20% VAT.\\\"\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bonhams\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bonhams\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bonhams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bonhams\"}, {\"begin\": 642, \"end\": 645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Value-added_tax\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0007391474352375e-14, \"text\": \"VAT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Value-added_tax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Value-added_tax\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Friday, the auction house announced the opposite: \\\"We will donate the buyer's premium to the Teenage Cancer Trust\\\".\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 766, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 744, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teenage_Cancer_Trust\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Teenage Cancer Trust\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teenage_Cancer_Trust\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teenage_Cancer_Trust\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brandler said he was \\\"thrilled\\\" that the charity would receive all the money paid for the charity lots.\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 870, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"Will other salesrooms follow suit and be more [transparent] in their descriptions?\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Related ArticlesPhillips Takes $54 M. from Modern and Contemporary Sale, Bonhams on the Move, Demand for Female Photographers Rising: Morning Links for November 20, 2025Bonhams to Open New US Flagship in New York's Historic Steinway Hall  SAY CHEESE!The photography festival Les Rencontres d'Arles is doing well, despite the hectic context of France's parliamentary elections, reportsLe Quotidien de l'art.\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1038, \"end\": 1045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bonhams\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bonhams\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bonhams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bonhams\"}, {\"begin\": 1099, \"end\": 1106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Early_Show\", \"score\": 0.9999305630551721, \"rank\": 6.944175764853492e-05, \"text\": \"Morning\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Early_Show\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Early_Show\"}, {\"begin\": 1308, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.131008433031208e-14, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's 55th edition, titled \\\"Beneath the Surface\\\", consists of 30 exhibitions (10 certified by the artistic direction).\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The event is always presented as an opportunity to discover Arles's heritage in a new light, as well as unusual spaces, such as the second floor of the city's Monoprix (the French equivalent of Target), which currently features the seven finalists of Fondation Roederer's D\\u00e9couverte prize.\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1550, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http:/