kid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kering\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kering\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Chapelle de la Charit\\u00e9 houses a spectacular cabinet of curiosities by Michel Medinger.\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sophie Calle took over a damp underground space, called Cryptoportiques, to showcase a series of decomposing photographs.\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2065, \"end\": 2077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Calle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sophie Calle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Calle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Calle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The idea is to speed up the decomposition process and help them disappear \\\"on a high note\\\".\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2278, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The festival runs through September 29.\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"THE DIGEST  Tanzanian portrait artistShadrack Chaulawas arrested for recording a viral video, showing him burning a photo of PresidentSamia Suluhu Hassanwhile verbally insulting her.\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2320, \"end\": 2330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digest_(Roman_law)\", \"score\": 0.999733575593091, \"rank\": 0.0002664002664003856, \"text\": \"THE DIGEST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digest_(Roman_law)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digest_(Roman_law)\"}, {\"begin\": 2332, \"end\": 2341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanzania\", \"score\": 0.9999999999763531, \"rank\": 2.251814926550944e-11, \"text\": \"Tanzanian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanzania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanzania\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 24-year-old painter has been sentenced to two years in prison or a fine of $2,000 (\\u00a31,600) after being found guilty of cybercrimes.\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2638, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some social media users have started an online drive to raise money to pay Chaula's fine so he can be freed from jail.\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"[BBC]  In an interview withThe Asia Pivot,Artnet Pro's biweekly members-only newsletter about Asia's art markets,Alice Lung, who overseeing thePerrotingallery's operations in Hong Kong, Shanghai, Tokyo, Seoul, and Los Angeles stated: \\\"From what I observed at the recently concluded Hong Kong auction sales, the Chinese contemporary art market appears particularly weak.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 3126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2758, \"end\": 2761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\", \"score\": 0.7940079257127438, \"rank\": 0.25943322694921883, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\"}, {\"begin\": 2870, \"end\": 2875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_and_Bob\", \"score\": 0.999984194469415, \"rank\": 1.5805780776401705e-05, \"text\": \"Alice\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_and_Bob\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_and_Bob\"}, {\"begin\": 2932, \"end\": 2941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9999999922192728, \"rank\": 7.762971123047707e-09, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}, {\"begin\": 2943, \"end\": 2951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5982906351155373e-14, \"text\": \"Shanghai\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\", \"dbpedia\": \"